author: alexdma
msg: - Session is cleared even when the refactoring job fails.

- All entity signatures retrieved from the Entity Hub or other sources are merged together before they are added to the session (TODO check if merging is "OWL-safe" e.g. it is not introducing one owl:Ontology resource too many).
- Small fixes in resource release during deactivation (TODO I think this type of deactivation could be too aggressive).
Overall it should be safer, faster, occupy much less disk space and save some more lines of code.
